{"tid":1326543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小小提醒，搞清楚要針對新地同警察啲乜","createTime":"2019-07-17T09:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T09:14:51.000Z","uid":269930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0368cf20921fe1e6cce6fac1ae5b29c2337dcf2d","tid":1326543,"uid":269930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190717/s00001/1563301379081/6商場地契准警執法-包括太古新城市\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563301379081%2F6%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aubQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=2fe9ed7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00001%2F1563301379081%2F6%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%87%86%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82&h=31998982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190717/s00001/1563301379081/6商場地契准警執法-包括太古新城市</a><br />\n<br />\n其實警察的確係想做乜就做乜。只要有所謂既「合理」懷疑，警察無乜野係唔可以做，所以我地先話警權過大。<br />\n<br />\n所以警察唔係唔可以入商場，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔應該</span>入商場，騷擾到商戶、居民同遊客。知己知彼百戰百勝。唔好用錯理由投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78979e6f8782145f3e8ab61ebcfc32a588aeee12","tid":1326543,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"無辜市民都受到恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}